With this function you can set whether the browser window should capture all input (set it to <tt>false</tt>) or whether the game should capture the input (set it to <tt>true</tt>). Note that this function is for use with the HTML5 module only.
The above code sets the game to capture all browser input on the HTML5 target platform.
